mple.com','13AG8i9','Gather Mini Kegs','',2,1,-1,'Gather Minikegs with bungs/safety vent bungs&lt;br&gt;','[]','','',0,0,0,0,0,'gather3',1,0,'[]'),(89,'test@example.com','13AG8i9','Move fermentation bin','',2,2,-1,'If needed move the fermentation bin to a height suitable for bottling from. This should be carried out early to allow any disturbance to settle','[]','','',0,0,0,0,0,'',1,0,'[]'),(90,'test@example.com','13AG8i9','Clean Work Area','',2,3,-1,'Clean the entire work area with mild detergent. It is important to ensure the entire work area is clean before starting with bottling.','[]','','',0,0,0,0,0,'',1,0,'[]'),(91,'test@example.com','13AG8i9','Setup Work Area','',2,4,-1,'Setup the work area as shown in the image, cleaning the bottles may be carried out the previous evening to save time.','[\"bottlingsetup.png\"]','','',0,0,0,0,0,'',1,0,'[]'),(92,'test@example.com','13AG8i9','Clean Bottles','',2,5,-1,'Cleaning the bottles using hot water and detergent.','[]','','',0,0,0,0,0,'',1,0,'[]'),(93,'test@example.com','13AG8i9','Clean the bottles using a bottle brush to ensure no deposits are left in the bottle. Drain solution out of the bottles.','',2,5,0,'','[]','','',0,0,0,0,0,'',1,0,'[]'),(94,'test@example.com','13AG8i9','Rinse the bottles with a small amount of water.','',2,5,1,'','[]','','',0,0,0,0,0,'',1,0,'[]'),(95,'test@example.com','13AG8i9','Setup Work Area 2','',2,6,-1,'Setup the work area as show in the image, during the bottling stage all equipment will be required.','[\"bottlingsetup2.png\"]','','',0,0,0,0,0,'',1,0,'[]'),(96,'test@example.com','13AG8i9','Sterilise Crown Caps','',2,7,-1,'Crown caps needs to be sterilised before use.','[]','','',0,0,0,0,0,'',1,0,'[]'),(97,'test@example.com','13AG8i9','Boil 500ml of water and add to a clean pyrex jug','',2,7,0,'','[]','','',0,0,0,0,0,'',1,0,'[]'),(98,'test@example.com','13AG8i9','Add ...num_crown_caps... crown caps/plastic caps to the jug and set aside.','',2,7,1,'','[]','','',0,0,0,0,0,'',1,0,'[]'),(99,'t